messages.content:
@🔔 Events 

Hello folks! Hope you’re all doing well. We value your input and would love to hear your thoughts on our events moving forward. You’ll now notice that event threads will include a short feedback form for each event you participate in. Your feedback will ultimately help us improve our future events! 😎 

Keep your eyes peeled at the bottom of each thread for this survey: https://forms.gle/4ErKjZvx2RUKa8Rb8

Thanks in advance! We look forward to sharing many more events with you ✈️
